---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Cloutly — Which review tool wins for small business? | SocialProof" description="Comparing SocialProof and Cloutly for collecting and displaying reviews. See pricing, features, and which is better for your business." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/cloutly">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f1f5f9; color: #475569; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; padding: .4rem 1rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; letter-spacing: .04em; }
    section { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; font-size: 0.92rem; }
    .compare-table th { background: #f8fafc; padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .75rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:hover td { background: #fafafa; }
    .check { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 700; }
    .cross { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 700; }
    .neutral { color: #6b7280; }
    .highlight-row td { font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-badge { display: inline-block; background: #dcfce7; color: #16a34a; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; padding: .2rem .6rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-left: .5rem; }
    .summary-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .summary-card { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .summary-card.sp { border-color: #bfdbfe; background: #eff6ff; }
    .summary-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .summary-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem; }
    .summary-card ul li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .cta-block { text-align: center; background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .cta-block h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .cta-block p { color: #bfdbfe; max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #2563eb; padding: .9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; }
    .faq { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding: 1.25rem 0; }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .faq-item p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .compare-table { font-size: 0.82rem; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/vs/">Compare</a>
    <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <span class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs Cloutly</span>
  <h1>SocialProof vs Cloutly — which is right for your business?</h1>
  <p>Both tools help you collect reviews and display them online. But they're built for different needs. Here's an honest comparison so you can choose the one that actually fits.</p>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Side-by-side comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof <span class="winner-badge">our pick</span></th>
        <th>Cloutly</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr class="highlight-row">
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td class="check">Free forever (1 widget)</td>
        <td class="neutral">$29/month</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Embed widget on website</td>
        <td class="check">✓ All plans</td>
        <td class="check">✓ All plans</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Custom testimonial collection</td>
        <td class="check">✓ Yes</td>
        <td class="check">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Google Review import</td>
        <td class="check">✓ Yes</td>
        <td class="check">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Review request campaigns</td>
        <td class="neutral">Via shareable link</td>
        <td class="check">Email + SMS campaigns</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>AI review responses</td>
        <td class="cross">✗ No</td>
        <td class="check">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Reputation monitoring</td>
        <td class="cross">✗ No</td>
        <td class="check">✓ Multi-platform</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Widget customization</td>
        <td class="check">✓ Full branding</td>
        <td class="check">✓ Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Setup time</td>
        <td class="check">5 minutes</td>
        <td class="neutral">30–60 minutes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Target market</td>
        <td class="neutral">Small business, freelancers</td>
        <td class="neutral">Multi-location businesses</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="summary-grid">
    <div class="summary-card sp">
      <h3>🟦 Choose SocialProof if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Want to start free without a credit card</li>
        <li>Need a simple widget on your website in minutes</li>
        <li>Run a single-location or solo business</li>
        <li>Don't need full reputation management — just testimonials</li>
        <li>Want clean, minimal embeds that don't slow your site</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card">
      <h3>⬜ Consider Cloutly if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Have 5+ locations needing centralized review management</li>
        <li>Want automated email + SMS review request campaigns</li>
        <li>Need AI to draft responses to reviews at scale</li>
        <li>Can justify $29+/month for a full reputation platform</li>
        <li>Are a franchise or enterprise business</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>The bottom line</h2>
  <p style="color:#444; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1rem;">Cloutly is built for multi-location businesses that need centralized reputation management — think franchises, chains, dental groups. It's a solid platform if you need SMS campaigns and AI review responses and can pay $29+/month.</p>
  <p style="color:#444; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1rem;">SocialProof is built for small businesses and freelancers who need to collect testimonials and display them beautifully on their website — without the enterprise complexity or the enterprise price tag. If you're a solo practitioner, a local business, or an indie creator, SocialProof is the simpler, faster choice.</p>
  <p style="color:#444; line-height:1.7;">And it's free to start. No credit card required.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
  <div class="faq">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is SocialProof really free?</h3>
      <p>Yes. SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget with unlimited testimonials. You only upgrade if you need multiple widgets or advanced features. No trial period, no time limit.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I import reviews I already have?</h3>
      <p>Yes. You can import from Google Reviews or paste in testimonials you've already collected — DMs, emails, or messages from clients. No need to start from scratch.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Does SocialProof work for multi-location businesses?</h3>
      <p>Yes, though at scale Cloutly's centralized dashboard may be a better fit. SocialProof excels for single-location businesses and freelancers who want a fast, simple solution.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>How do I embed SocialProof on my website?</h3>
      <p>Copy your widget script tag from the dashboard and paste it into your website's HTML. Works with Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, Webflow, and any custom site. Setup takes about 5 minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="cta-block">
    <h2>Try SocialProof free — no credit card needed</h2>
    <p>Set up your testimonial widget in 5 minutes. Free forever for 1 widget.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-btn">Get started free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/vs/" style="color:#999">All comparisons</a> · <a href="/pricing" style="color:#999">Pricing</a> · <a href="/privacy" style="color:#999">Privacy</a></p>
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/ecommerce" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Ecommerce</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
